		Today if we look around computers are everywhere, in every nook and corner of the country.
		Computer programming basically means explaining to a computer what you want it to do for you.
		Since computer is a machine, we have to define everything that it does. Sometimes programming or coding seems to be very laborious
		or boring if one does not understand how it is to be done correctly, but once a person learns how to do it, it may appear to be 
		a talent and you may develop a craze for it.
		<br>
		<br>
		As a child i was always amazed by the cartoons on TV and wondered how Shaktimaan could fly. Unknowingly I was already
		attracted to the things one can do with the help of a computer. Later as a growing boy I was more interested in the operating Systems 
		used in the mobile phones and how those terrific video games worked.
		<br>
		<br>
		In the first year of my degree college all my doubts were cleared and I came in contact with various technologies that made all these possible.
