Each has its own advantages and limitations.
	The language Visual Basic is used on Windows PC. My favourite language is PHP, It is one of the best, opensource programming language used on the web.
	It is used by all mojor web apps including facebook, google, twitter and many more. Whenever we search something on Google or hit a like on a friend's facebook post we are actually interacting with a php script.
	<br><br>
	One of the most widespread rumors about computer science or programming is that you have to learn this whole bulk of information before you start. I think its a very wrong notion.
	Instaed you can start with what you already know. If you have a clear idea of what you want to make and a perfect plan, then you need to solve doubt there are always books available and of course Google saves.
	<br><br>
	Each day new opportunities are evolving for the youth and most of them come from computer world. Computesr are present everywhere, hospitals, museums, railway stations, schools, shopping malls almost all corners of the city.
	
